title: Joe Seul - Psycho Tropics
description:
Joe Seul - Psycho Tropics

1. Warm Liquid Goo Phase
2. Sarasota, Florida
3. Growing Up
4. We Could Split A Mango
5. Mmmkay Ultra
6. Bee Here Now
7. Doom Sauce
8. Clouds Coming Home
9. Super Delicious
10. Raindrops 

Credits:

Written, recorded, produced, and arranged by Joe Seul in Sarasota, FL, USA
Mixed by Michael Regina in Sarasota, FL, USA
Mastered by Will Manning at Chase Park Transduction in Athens, GA, USA

Release Date: September 6th, 2015
Length: 43 Minutes
Website: www.joeseul.com

Info: 

Joe Seul's full-length debut, "Psycho Tropics" meets the listener in a dreamy Sarasota, Florida of for a journey through space, time, feelings, and all sorts of other weird vibrations. 

RIYL: M83, Radiohead, Animal Collective, Smashing Pumpkins

Reviews:

"A mostly-intrapersonal modern electro-psych-rock odyssey that is as tasty as it is refreshing." - Neil Legstrom, The Wilmington Gazette 

"This record makes me want to shrink down to the size of a baseball and go surfing inside of a watermelon. By the time I'm halfway through each full listening, I am soaking wet and my mental problems are laid out in front of me like a bowl full of grapes." - Devyn Blair, BlazeIt Magazine

"Seul has created a monster. Psycho Tropics is a magic carpet ride through a sprawling paradise; with a comical lightness that bookends its paranoid, doomy center." - Daniel Bojangle (Street Magician)
